Understory includes Lonicera subspicata, Eriogonum fasciculatum, Eriogonum wrightii membranaceum, and Garrya flavescens. Stream with scattered Salix lasiolepis and Fraxinus velutina.

Arkose substrate with a sandy soil; aspects S, E, N; slope 0-120%.
